{"tid":710624,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"張敬軒15號演唱會一事睇到香港觀眾風氣有幾差","createTime":"2018-06-21T02:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T08:31:44.000Z","uid":14075,"like":50,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"980ee79ee15dfde4f7ea2004789ecb02c57b9ed1","tid":710624,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"演唱會標準時間向來都係8:30-11:00。<br />\nEncore本意向來只係bonus, 只係香港觀眾麻鳩煩所以圈內潛規則run down要做個一早定好左既encore，用黎滿足下班聽眾，本身呢樣野已經扭曲左。而家15號晚張敬軒做足哂兩樣野11:10 完場就要比狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n2nd encore本身唔包有既野又比人屌到一定要有咁，仲有人話外國歌手點點點，又唔睇下班外國歌手係可以唱90分鐘10點鐘就完show。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲下係咪要rundown度又cut番幾個字出黎搞預定既2nd encore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持軒仔無視15號怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808567b14caa5dcdf57d1d401f26a7f4152efd3f","tid":710624,"uid":182286,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e22bf58998bc26f4838fc931836d70b59b2f74e","tid":710624,"uid":5460,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"on9歌手 配 on9 fans"},{"pid":"f0f0985d2b94e39b15ab80cab8578c63d14ffdb8","tid":710624,"uid":182286,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2a3aab3248ccb5bed4ed0df3141b5f7ff5e0d4b","tid":710624,"uid":706,"like":22,"dislike":11,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"張敬軒屌得好啱<br />\n依班兒登垃圾真係同啲大陸喱一樣都係生蕃<br />\n要不是我來睇你演唱會 你早就完蛋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心啦 知唔知醜呀 同大陸西一撚樣既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b37bf32683b6cceb7368d3aa89439faeea471c2","tid":710624,"uid":36008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"808567b14caa5dcdf57d1d401f26a7f4152efd3f","tid":710624,"uid":182286,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入場睇一個performance<br />\n係睇佢努力嘅成果㗎</span>"},{"pid":"f251f6df8e1794d06a0c8b5d8d5476e2646f84ad","tid":710624,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"外國啲演唱會得90min 仲要未必有encore"},{"pid":"f482f6e3500a9cf101ea704e9e735040b3450c4c","tid":710624,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"睇得出佢有心做音樂<br />\n做好音樂唔係為左迎合觀眾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481fcbdcac8990bf659639d528af47fe3d2ca238","tid":710624,"uid":70943,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"15號晚觀眾不滿係ok<br />\n但日日開十幾個post屌哂老母仲話自己唔係怨婦<br />\n人地蝗國fans都識話尊重自己idol 會想了解個show背後嘅message<br />\n班怨婦一味就識得屌人妖show<br />\n最好軒叔跟哂自己意願 做佢地嘅扯線公仔就最好<br />\n請自己老死胡定欣上台又唔撚得 仲走去屌人地<br />\n第一次見識咁閪嘅觀眾"},{"pid":"2b6d83fc959682aed83403d785df3c4205d3b9cd","tid":710624,"uid":5995,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"唱越南文歌以為自己好好笑個下先正"},{"pid":"4330df42e1fe8c831b38374b037ba747a72f9a83","tid":710624,"uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f251f6df8e1794d06a0c8b5d8d5476e2646f84ad","tid":710624,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"外國啲演唱會得90min 仲要未必有encore"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"兒登d細路未睇過唔知呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b6159020ed7c42b93cc5b523e28e983d8303da","tid":710624,"uid":15935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4330df42e1fe8c831b38374b037ba747a72f9a83","tid":710624,"uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f251f6df8e1794d06a0c8b5d8d5476e2646f84ad","tid":710624,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"外國啲演唱會得90min 仲要未必有encore"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"兒登d細路未睇過唔知呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:15:30.000Z","msg":"你講埋呢啲嘢無助理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申頭場觀眾"},{"pid":"4bd631ce33e87366b527620344604f5d51b1d109","tid":710624,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b6159020ed7c42b93cc5b523e28e983d8303da","tid":710624,"uid":15935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4330df42e1fe8c831b38374b037ba747a72f9a83","tid":710624,"uid":14075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f251f6df8e1794d06a0c8b5d8d5476e2646f84ad","tid":710624,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"外國啲演唱會得90min 仲要未必有encore"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"兒登d細路未睇過唔知呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:15:30.000Z","msg":"你講埋呢啲嘢無助理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申頭場觀眾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"外國歌手呢個point係其他post 15號觀眾講的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/